  "detailed_description": "<strong>Car Wash TD, a simple one-of-a-kind tower defense game.</strong><br><strong>Goal: wash cars before they reach the end of the road.</strong><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1732660/extras/d2bf453f67f89032623f930e74838075.poster.avif?t=1642794713\" width=600 height=234 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1732660/extras/d2bf453f67f89032623f930e74838075.webm?t=1642794713\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1732660/extras/d2bf453f67f89032623f930e74838075.mp4?t=1642794713\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br>You have been hired by the government to create a system that washes cars directly on the road. To achieve your mandate, you have at your disposal water turrets of many kinds and many more advanced technologies.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1732660/extras/86ead34fbd4c3c196ebccdb80be125cf.avif?t=1642794713\" width=625 height=90 /></span><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1732660/extras/319e00109199fcf5568ee1912cde9e86.poster.avif?t=1642794713\" width=600 height=234 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1732660/extras/319e00109199fcf5568ee1912cde9e86.webm?t=1642794713\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1732660/extras/319e00109199fcf5568ee1912cde9e86.mp4?t=1642794713\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br>Unleash your creativity and puzzle solving skills by creating mazes to make the path of the cars longer and increase the efficiency of your towers. Don’t worry about causing traffic, cleaning cars is your priority.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1732660/extras/bebe7d2fe6b01b8615cc87a7f5b2406f.avif?t=1642794713\" width=625 height=90 /></span><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1732660/extras/114fecf5728805b9c3043791d3e1c528.poster.avif?t=1642794713\" width=600 height=236 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1732660/extras/114fecf5728805b9c3043791d3e1c528.webm?t=1642794713\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1732660/extras/114fecf5728805b9c3043791d3e1c528.mp4?t=1642794713\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1732660/extras/e73f86a054191c760acf58d8e2653cf5.avif?t=1642794713\" width=625 height=90 /></span><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1732660/extras/d49412085cc5b4de71bb9676c9363938.poster.avif?t=1642794713\" width=600 height=234 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1732660/extras/d49412085cc5b4de71bb9676c9363938.webm?t=1642794713\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1732660/extras/d49412085cc5b4de71bb9676c9363938.mp4?t=1642794713\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1732660/extras/9eb0f600d56866cf03e4fdd9f3741952.avif?t=1642794713\" width=625 height=9